<subSubSection type="etymology">
<paragraph pageNumber="10">Etymology: The specific epithet is a patronym honoring Marcelo T. Tavares, professor and researcher of Chalcididae at Universidade Federal do Espirito Santo, Brazil.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
